* GF180MCU-D textbook-style two-stage single-ended RF PA seed.
* Pins: gnda vdda rfin rfout vbias
* Stage 1 is an ideal-current-biased common-source driver.
* Stage 2 is a larger common-source output stage with a finite-Q output match.
* Status: runnable seed, but not layout/passive signoff.
.subckt {{netlist_name}} gnda vdda rfin rfout vbias

* Driver stage.
MDRV drv_d drv_gate gnda gnda nfet_03v3.12 l={{ MDRV_L }}u w={{ MDRV_W }}u m={{ MDRV_M }}
CIN rfin drv_gate {{ Cin_value }}
RBDRV drv_gate vbias {{ Rbiasdrv_value }}
IBDRV vdda drv_d 0.8m
RDRVLEAK drv_d gnda 1G

* Interstage coupling and damping.
CINTER drv_d out_gate {{ Cinter_value }}
RGOUT out_gate gate {{ Rgout_value }}
RBOUT gate vbias {{ Rbiasout_value }}

* Final output stage.
MOUT drain gate gnda gnda nfet_03v3.12 l={{ MOUT_L }}u w={{ MOUT_W }}u m={{ MOUT_M }}
IBOUT vdda drain 8m

* AC-coupled output match seed, adapted from the single-stage AB template.
CBLOCK drain nmatch 100p
RNMATCH nmatch gnda 1G
RCSER nmatch nmatch_cser 1.73
CSER nmatch_cser rfout 7.351p
RLSHUNT rfout lshunt_top 5.77
LSHUNT lshunt_top gnda 73.511n

* Optional harmonic traps: series-resonant shunts near H2 and H3.
RLH2 rfout h2trap_l {{ Rh2_value }}
LH2 h2trap_l h2trap {{ Lh2_value }}
RCH2 h2trap h2trap_c {{ Rh2c_value }}
CH2 h2trap_c gnda {{ Ch2_value }}
RLH3 rfout h3trap_l {{ Rh3_value }}
LH3 h3trap_l h3trap {{ Lh3_value }}
RCH3 h3trap h3trap_c {{ Rh3c_value }}
CH3 h3trap_c gnda {{ Ch3_value }}

.ends {{netlist_name}}
